Text: Re AppointmentGreat I sincerely appreciate you help and will confirm with Dean Streetman today and get back to you Ken Dickerson

AppointmentKen Ben Streetman Dean of the UT School of Engineering tells me that he will be in Houston on November and would like to meet with you I realize that your schedule is overflowing these days however should time permit the Dean would sincerely appreciate an opportunity to visit with you for a few minutes Thank you Kenneth R Dickerson
